      <title>新加坡执政党党员易华兰辞去部长职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/singapore-transport-minister-iswaran-resigns-after-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新加坡总理李显龙的声明，新加坡的易华兰于 1 月 16 日辞去内阁部长和执政的人民行动党成员的职务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/singapore-transport-minister-iswaran-resigns-after-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 01:56:18 GMT</pubDate>
