    <item>
      <title>美国因腐败禁止危地马拉前总统入境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/us-bars-ex-guatemalan-president-from-entry-due-to-corruption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院周三在一份声明中表示，由于危地马拉前总统亚历杭德罗·贾马泰参与“严重腐败”，美国已禁止他入境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/us-bars-ex-guatemalan-president-from-entry-due-to-corruption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 01:46:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着胡塞武装船只袭击持续，美国对也门发动更多袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/us-unleashes-more-yemen-strikes-as-houthi-ship-attacks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国官员称，随着胡塞武装继续袭击红海航运，美国连夜对也门 14 个胡塞武装目标发动了新一轮袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/us-unleashes-more-yemen-strikes-as-houthi-ship-attacks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 01:42:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡交通部长因贪污指控辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/singapore-transport-minister-appears-in-court-after-graft-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡交通部长易华兰 (S. Iswaran) 在被指控腐败后辞职，这是近四十年来袭击这个城市国家的最大政治丑闻的最新进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/singapore-transport-minister-appears-in-court-after-graft-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jan 2024 00:18:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国寻求在达沃斯会见亚马逊和 Alphabet 高管，推动技术推广</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-18/uk-s-hunt-to-meet-amazon-alphabet-execs-in-davos-in-tech-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特计划周四在达沃斯会见亚马逊公司和 Alphabet 公司高管，作为推动英国科技行业投资的一部分。]]></description>
